data.description: Up to $1,500 in SELLER PAID Closing Costs!! Meticulously maintained two-story home. Step through the front door into a move-in ready haven with new Luxury Vinyl Plank flooring throughout the main floor. The Great Room, with tons of natural light, connects to the Kitchen and dining area ideal for social gatherings. The Kitchen features elegant espresso cabinetry, granite countertops, and a large pantry. A half bath and a mudroom with storage options are conveniently located on the first floor. The second floor hosts the Primary Suite sanctuary, with a tray ceiling, walk-In Closet, and a private bath with a soaking tub, shower, and double granite vanity. Three additional bedrooms on second floor, each with unique design potential, share a bathroom with a granite-top vanity. Outside, a covered patio in the fully fenced backyard offers a perfect space for outdoor activities and personal landscaping touches. This home is not just a residence but a foundation for lifelong memories. Located near downtown Columbia and Lexington, and just minutes from Columbia Metropolitan Airport. Make this your new home today!
